title: Aslan Tautiyev
text:
Aslan Kazikovich Tautiyev (; born 25 May 1990) is a Russian former <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="Defender%20%28association%20football%29">defender</a>.
Club career.
He played two seasons in the <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> for <a href="FC%20Volgar%20Astrakhan">FC Volgar Astrakhan</a>.
